1.1 Estimation of gene expression enrichment between germline and other lineages

mavg_segregationDF %>% filter(Class %in% c("gAsym_polyadenylation","g_localised")) %>% 
  rowwise() %>%
  mutate(ecto_mix = mean(c(Ep,Er,El), na.rm=TRUE),
         g2ect = (g+0.001)/(ecto_mix+0.001),
         g2end = (g+0.001)/(en+0.001),
         g2mes = (g+0.001)/(mean(c(Mav,mr,ml, na.rm=TRUE)) + 0.001),
         g2mav = (g+0.001)/(Mav+0.001)) %>%
  select(gene_id,g2mav,g2ect,g2mes,g2end) %>%
  pivot_longer(!gene_id) %>%
  ggplot(aes(y=value,x=name)) + 
  geom_boxplot() + ylim(0,20) +   stat_summary(fun = mean, color = "red") +
  stat_summary(
    fun.min = function(x) mean(x) - sd(x)*1, 
    fun.max = function(x) mean(x) + sd(x)*2, #Add 2sd to the upper limit
    geom = "errorbar",
    color = "red",
    width = .3
  )

1.2 Use ectoderm as an antagonist proxy to identify germline-specific markers

#Transcripts enriched in g and depleted in ectodermal lineage. Use only already defined as g-biased durin 4-8 transition
g_specific_1 <- mavg_segregationDF %>% filter(Class %in% c("gAsym_polyadenylation","g_localised")) %>% 
  rowwise() %>%
  mutate(ecto_mix = mean(c(Ep,Er,El), na.rm=TRUE),
         g2ect = (g+0.001)/(ecto_mix+0.001),
         g2end = (g+0.001)/(en+0.001),
         g2mes = (g+0.001)/(mean(c(Mav,mr,ml, na.rm=TRUE)) + 0.001),
         g2mav = (g+0.001)/(Mav+0.001)) %>%
  filter(g2ect >= 7 & g > 20)#%>% pull(gene_id) %>% View()

g_specific_2 <- mavg_segregationDF %>% filter(Class %in% c("gAsym_polyadenylation","g_localised")) %>% 
  rowwise() %>%
  mutate(ecto_mix = mean(c(Ep,Er,El), na.rm=TRUE),
         g2ect = (g+0.001)/(ecto_mix+0.001),
         g2end = (g+0.001)/(en+0.001),
         g2mes = (g+0.001)/(mean(c(Mav,mr,ml, na.rm=TRUE)) + 0.001),
         g2mav = (g+0.001)/(Mav+0.001)) %>%
  filter((g2mav >= 2.5 & g2end >= 1 & g2ect >= 4 & g > 20)  %>% replace_na(TRUE))#%>% pull(gene_id) %>% View()

#G-specific compared to all blastomeres

g_specific_3 <- mavg_segregationDF %>% filter(Class %in% c("gAsym_polyadenylation","g_localised")) %>% 
  rowwise() %>%
  mutate(ecto_mix = mean(c(Ep,Er,El), na.rm=TRUE),
         all_mix  = mean(c(Mav,mr,ml,Ep,Er,El,en), na.rm=TRUE),
         g2all = (g+0.001)/(all_mix+0.001)) %>% filter(g2all >= 2 & g > 20) %>% arrange(desc(g2all))
   #ggplot(aes(x=g2all)) + geom_boxplot()

g_specific_final <- rbind(g_specific_1,g_specific_2) %>% distinct()

#write.table(g_specific_final,"g_specific_final.tsv",row.names = F,col.names = T,quote = F,sep = "\t")
